metadata.name: RAXworld Tribute Mystery Box #2
metadata.description: RAXworld is proud to launch its most exclusive and premium asset yet ‘The Tribute’. Your mystery box contains 1 of 5 RAXworld Tributes each with their own unique design, rarity and specialties. We’ve chosen 5 of the most elite skateboarders to kickstart our collection of Metaverse-ready assets, that grant owners VIP features, additional assets including skateboards, helmets and clothing, and premium access to RAXworld’s Arena. Use your Tribute in the Arena to access the Sports worlds and test your skills, watch live events in The Stadium, shop and explore limited edition items in RAXworld Central, and interact with your favourite athletes in the Villages.
